PropertyPackage.ComponentDescription: Property Package that uses the Peng-Robinson EOS. Recommended for use with hydrocarbons and non-condensables. The properties are calculated directly from the EOS and/or experimental data, except: Liquid Density: Rackett Method Liquid Thermal Conductivity: Latini et al Method Vapor Thermal Conductivity: Ely-Hanley Method Liquid Surface Tension: Brock-Bird Method
